## Your task — phased synthesis

Target: **score > {{ "%.4f"|format(baseline_score) if baseline_score is not none else "baseline" }}**

| Phase | Deliverable |
|-------|-------------|
| **Proposal 1** | Pick one **synthesis seed** or **co-occurrence combo** + ≥{{ min_new_positive_rules }} missing positive patterns; submit and read feedback |
| **Proposal 2** | Alternative architecture (different seed/combo), still ≥{{ min_new_positive_rules }} missing patterns |
| **Proposal 3** | Refine the better of 1/2 (parameter or structure tweak) |

Rules:
- Write `candidate.py`, run `python submit.py candidate.py` after each change.
- If a submission scores below baseline, **change architecture** (not just constants on the same IIR/smooth_rec stack).
- Use remaining quota to iterate on the best synthesis direction.

